      • enter

        public void enter(java.lang.String id,
         Entry entry)
           throws java.lang.Exception
        Enters an id together with an entry into this SymbolTable using the current scope level. The entry's level is set to currentLevel().
        Throws:
        SymbolTableException - when there is no valid current scope level, or when the id is already declared on the current level.
        java.lang.Exception
